column5: hello all does anybody know the date as i am unable to find my book and i want to set aside that weekend thanks jamie.[huntsville area]
last saturday in April. Same as its been for ever.

As with most things on the net. Double check the "experts".  Huntsville is in region 15  Brook Trout and lake trout: Jan 1- Sept 30 Brown trout and rainbow trout: All year Check the exceptions ie Algonquin park and the like.  Hope this link works  http://www.mnr.gov.on.ca/MNR/pubs/fishing/...y/Zone%2015.pdf
